"""Test format_time_input no start time specified."""
five_mins_ago = self.time_now - pc.ONE_MINUTE * 5
with mock.patch.object(self.perf, 'extract_timestamp_keys', return_value=(
    five_mins_ago, None)) as mck_get_time:
    start_time, end_time = self.perf.format_time_input(self.p_data.array,
        pc.ARRAY, end_time=self.time_now)
    mck_get_time.assert_called_once_with(array_id=self.p_data.array,
        category=pc.ARRAY, director_id=None, key_tgt_id=None)
    self.assertIsInstance(start_time, str)
    self.assertIsInstance(end_time, str)
    self.assertEqual(start_time, str(five_mins_ago))
    self.assertEqual(end_time, str(self.time_now))
